data.name: sqlSelectCommand2.CommandText
data.value: SELECT dep.Description AS DepositType, sh.INVOICE_DATE AS DepositDate, ad.AMOUNT AS DepositAmount, ad.BALANCE FROM AR_DEPOSIT AS ad INNER JOIN AR_PAYMENT_DETAIL AS pd ON pd.CASH_JOURNAL_ID = ad.CASH_JOURNAL_ID AND pd.CASH_JOURNAL_LINE = ad.CASH_JOURNAL_LINE AND pd.ENTRY_NUMBER = ad.ENTRY_NUMBER INNER JOIN SO_TRN_HDR AS sh ON sh.INVOICE_ID = pd.INVOICE_ID AND ad.agreement_id = sh.agreement_id INNER JOIN LD_Deposits AS dep ON dep.Deposit_ID = sh.deposit_id INNER JOIN SO_TYPE AS t ON t.SO_TYPE_ID = sh.SO_TYPE_ID WHERE (t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LD' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LDP' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LPD' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LSRD') AND (sh.agreement_id = @agreement_id) AND (ISNULL(ad.BALANCE, 0) <> 0)

data.name: sqlSelectCommand3.CommandText
data.value: SELECT t.DESCRIPTION AS Type, h.INVOICE_DATE, h.INVOICENO, d.DESCRIPTION, h.TOTAL_PRODUCTS AS Amount, h.TOTAL_GST AS GST, h.TOTAL_SALES_TAXES AS PST, h.ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT AS ExtendedAmount, h.BALANCE, d.GL_ACCOUNT_NUMBER AS GLAccount FROM SO_TRN_HDR AS h INNER JOIN SO_TYPE AS t ON t.SO_TYPE_ID = h.SO_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SO_TRN_DETAIL AS d ON d.SO_TRN_ID = h.SO_TRN_ID WHERE (t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LS' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LD' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LDP' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LSA' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LPD' OR t.SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LSRD') AND (h.agreement_id = @agreement_id)

data.name: sqlSelectCommand4.CommandText
data.value: SELECT TRANSACTION_DATE AS PaymentDate, CHECK_NUMBER, PAYMENT_AMOUNT AS CheckAmount, COMMENT, CASE WHEN isnull(ph.BATCH_STAT, 'I') = 'I' THEN 'F' ELSE 'T' END AS Updated, DEPOSIT_NO FROM AR_PAYMENT_HEADERS AS ph WHERE (agreement_id = @agrement_id)

data.name: sqlSelectCommand5.CommandText
data.value: SELECT adj.LotAdjCode AS Code, adj.DESCRIPTION, adj.CostRecoverable, adj.AMOUNT, adj.GST_AMOUNT, adj.PST_AMOUNT, adj.ADJ_AMOUNT, adj.GL_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, adj.INVOICENO, lv1.lv1_code + ' ' + lv1.lv1_desc AS Level1, lv2.lv2_code + ' ' + lv2.lv2_desc AS Level2, lv3.lv3_code + ' ' + lv3.lv3_desc AS Level3, lv4.lv4_code + ' ' + lv4.lv4_desc AS Level4, CASE WHEN ISNULL(adj.LEM_COMP, '') = 'L' THEN 'Labor' WHEN ISNULL(adj.LEM_COMP, '') = 'E' THEN 'Equipment' WHEN ISNULL(adj.LEM_COMP, '') = 'M' THEN 'Material' WHEN ISNULL(adj.LEM_COMP, '') = 'O' THEN 'Other' WHEN ISNULL(adj.LEM_COMP, '') = 'S' THEN 'SubContract' ELSE '' END AS LemComponent, adj.ExtendedDescription FROM AR_ADJUSTMENTS AS adj INNER JOIN SO_TRN_HDR AS sh ON sh.INVOICE_ID = adj.INVOICE_ID Left Outer JOIN Level1_Codes AS lv1 ON lv1.lv1ID = adj.lv1ID LEFT OUTER JOIN Level2_Codes AS lv2 ON lv2.lv2ID = adj.lv2ID LEFT OUTER JOIN Level3_Codes AS lv3 ON lv3.lv3ID = adj.lv3ID LEFT OUTER JOIN Level4_Codes AS lv4 ON lv4.lv4ID = adj.lv4ID WHERE (sh.agreement_id = @agreement_id)and IsNull(adj.LotAdjCode,'') <> ''

data.name: sqlSelectCommand6.CommandText
data.value: SELECT INVOICE_DATE, ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT, BALANCE, SO_TRN_ID, SO_ID FROM SO_TRN_HDR WHERE (SO_TYPE_ID IN (SELECT SO_TYPE_ID FROM SO_TYPE AS st WHERE (SO_TYPE_CODE = 'LPI'))) AND (agreement_id = @agreement_id)

data.value: UPDATE [SO_TRN_HDR] SET [INVOICE_DATE] = @INVOICE_DATE, [ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT] = @p1, [BALANCE] = @BALANCE, [SO_TRN_ID] = @SO_TRN_ID, [SO_ID] = @SO_ID WHERE (((@IsNull_INVOICE_DATE = 1 AND [INVOICE_DATE] IS NULL) OR ([INVOICE_DATE] = @Original_INVOICE_DATE)) AND ((@p3 = 1 AND [ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT] IS NULL) OR ([ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT] = @p2)) AND ((@IsNull_BALANCE = 1 AND [BALANCE] IS NULL) OR ([BALANCE] = @Original_BALANCE)) AND ([SO_TRN_ID] = @Original_SO_TRN_ID) AND ([SO_ID] = @Original_SO_ID)); SELECT INVOICE_DATE, ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT, BALANCE, SO_TRN_ID, SO_ID FROM SO_TRN_HDR WHERE (SO_ID = @SO_ID) AND (SO_TRN_ID = @SO_TRN_ID)

data.value: DELETE FROM [SO_TRN_HDR] WHERE (((@IsNull_INVOICE_DATE = 1 AND [INVOICE_DATE] IS NULL) OR ([INVOICE_DATE] = @Original_INVOICE_DATE)) AND ((@p3 = 1 AND [ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT] IS NULL) OR ([ORIGINAL_INV_AMOUNT] = @p2)) AND ((@IsNull_BALANCE = 1 AND [BALANCE] IS NULL) OR ([BALANCE] = @Original_BALANCE)) AND ([SO_TRN_ID] = @Original_SO_TRN_ID) AND ([SO_ID] = @Original_SO_ID))

data.name: sqlSelectCommand7.CommandText
data.value: select s.Code,s.Description,d.AmountDiscounted from PROJ_LOT_AGREEMENT_DISCOUNTS d join LD_Discounts s on s.LD_Discounts_ID = d.LD_Discounts_ID where d.invoice_id is not null and d.unsoldReversed =0 and d.agreement_id = @agreement_id
